						               													<description>A Gigantik charades game for kids! It's a play of words!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The curtain is going up on Theatrix!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Theatrix is a game of charades developed by educators with children in mind. Theatrix gives your children the ability to use their imagination to act out what is on their card. Each card is divided into 4 categories: things we do, everyday things, things we use to move on and characters &amp;amp; creatures. When selecting a card, the child can use either the 400 words or the easily recognizable full-color illustrations, without the use of reading.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Gigantic floor gameboard creates a fun atmosphere for playing Theatrix, allowing the child the freedom and space to &amp;quot;play&amp;quot; out their turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Theatrix is the game that allows parents to sit back and enjoy the show! (Popcorn not included.)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the back of the box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
